extendedData.name: OracleText
extendedData.value:
Return to the iconic plane of Tarkir for an epic battle between dragons and clans. As powerful dragonstorms spiral Tarkir into chaos and wild dragons darken the skies, the five clans fight alongside their new Spirit Dragons for supremacy over the land. Discover which clan fits your playstyle with Tarkir’s distinct three-color gameplay.
Get ready to take back the skies with a box full of 9 Play Boosters, 15 foil lands, a foil bundle card, and an oversized spindown.
Contents:
• 9 Tarkir: Dragonstorm Play Boosters; each Play Booster contains 14 Magic: The Gathering cards
• 1 Traditional Foil card with Bundle-exclusive alternate-art
• 15 Traditional Foil basic lands
• 15 nonfoil basic lands
• 1 oversized Spindown life counter
• 1 card storage box
• 2 reference cards

Collector Boosters are the best way to open the most coveted cards and fiercest dragons. Each Collector Booster contains Rares and/or Mythics, Traditional Foils, Full-Art lands, and more. You could also open one of 500 Serialized headliner cards. Serialized headliner cards are localized in English only and are available in Tarkir: Dragonstorm Collector Boosters of any language.
Contents:
• 12 Tarkir: Dragonstorm Collector Boosters; each Collector Booster contains 15 Magic: The Gathering cards
• Each Collector booster may contain these cards: TDM 1–276, 287–419; TDC 1–10, 51-90; SPG 104–118
• Each Collector Booster includes 9–11 Traditional Foil cards
• 5 cards of rarity Rare or higher
• 3–5 Uncommon
• 4–6 Common
• 1 Land card
• Headliner card in <1% of boosters
